    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the COU decision of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index prediction error of 8.3% is well within the 15% acceptance threshold, and GCI values confirm adequate discretization convergence across all operating points.",
